  "prompt": "Which is the best training institute for spoken English in Pune?",
  "response": "There are several reputable institutes for spoken English training in Pune. While the \"best\" can vary based on individual preferences, here are some well-known options:\n\n1. **Inlingua**: Known for its interactive teaching methods and a strong emphasis on speaking skills. They offer various courses tailored to different proficiency levels.\n\n2. **British Council**: A globally recognized institution that provides comprehensive English language courses with a focus on speaking and communication skills.\n\n3. **Spoken English Classes Pune (SECP)**: Offers personalized coaching and small batch sizes to ensure focused learning. They have various courses catering to different needs.\n\n4. **Eureka English Academy**: Offers courses designed to enhance spoken English skills, focusing on practical conversation and business communication.\n\n5. **Language Curry**: A language learning platform that provides English speaking courses along with app-based resources for additional practice.\n\n6. **Mindspark**: Known for its engaging teaching methods and a focus on real-life conversation practice.\n\n7. **The English Academy**: Offers a variety of courses, including spoken English, and is known for its experienced trainers.\n\nWhen choosing an institute, consider factors like the curriculum, teaching methodology, reviews from past students, location, and fees. It may also be helpful to attend a trial class if available, to see if the teaching style suits you.",
